### Solving the Overpopulation of Spotted Lanternflies Issue at NY Vineyards

We are solving the issue of spotted lanternflies' presence in grape collection bins at vineyards. Spotted lanternflies contain certain chemicals that can spoil a grape yield as large as a thousand pounds! Follow along through the different steps of our specialized spotted lanternfly vacuum design to see how we tackled this issue.

